snippet.title: EVE Online: Tyrannis Trailer
snippet.description:
The latest trailer for the upcoming EVE Online : Tyrannis expansion which will be released in May 2010.

Find out more about EVE Online: Tyrannis here: http://www.eveonline.com/tyrannis/

Download the trailer here: http://www.eveonline.com/tyrannis/videos.asp?vid=2
